2009-10-17 23:39 UTC-0500 Vicente Guerra <vicente@guerra.com.mx>
  * source/debug/tbrwtext.prg
    * Changed Text2Array() to fix line changes when EOL is CR+LF
      (hb_atokens() doesn't support delimiters with more than
      one character long).

